Wenwen Wang wrote:
> 
> In snd_hda_parse_generic_codec(), 'spec' is allocated through kzalloc().
> Then, the pin widgets in 'codec' are parsed. However, if the parsing
> process fails, 'spec' is not deallocated, leading to a memory leak.
